    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/586601ac99640ab2bb56780adf94eb04.poster.avif?t=1771370151\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/586601ac99640ab2bb56780adf94eb04.webm?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/586601ac99640ab2bb56780adf94eb04.mp4?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>At Night</i></strong> 是一款以深夜电视节目形式呈现的章节式心理恐怖游戏。每一集都由一位幸存者讲述自己经历的创伤事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本集《<strong>The Nurse</strong>》中，玩家将跟随护士 Emily Collins，她接受了一份在 Bloomring Hospital 的夜班工作。原本看似普通的值班，很快便因医院显露出的异常而变得令人不安。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>她活了下来。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>而现在，她开始讲述自己的故事。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/897e02e4a75d4b5078a77cd5376139ba.poster.avif?t=1771370151\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/897e02e4a75d4b5078a77cd5376139ba.webm?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/897e02e4a75d4b5078a77cd5376139ba.mp4?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/ae7003bd30d36f716b9f6ecbb8857818.poster.avif?t=1771370151\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/ae7003bd30d36f716b9f6ecbb8857818.webm?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/ae7003bd30d36f716b9f6ecbb8857818.mp4?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以氛围营造与探索为核心的第一人称叙事体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同地点之间驾车往返</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接收文字信息</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与患者交谈并提供帮助</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拾取并使用物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在值班期间探索医院</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作主要为步行模拟类型，玩家的选择将影响故事的最终走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖与剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/71d7225eea2d16c820dc555736a16266.poster.avif?t=1771370151\" width=720 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/71d7225eea2d16c820dc555736a16266.webm?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306160/extras/71d7225eea2d16c820dc555736a16266.mp4?t=1771370151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>At Night</i></strong> 通过环境叙事、沉浸式讲述以及黑暗而风格化的美术设计，呈现出循序渐进的心理恐怖体验。故事以谜团为核心展开，并根据玩家的选择提供多个结局</p>",
